data.description: VERY Motivated seller! Priced under market value! Open to All offers! This charming home in Clarksville is ready for a new family! You’re welcomed into this spacious house by an open floor plan that extends from the entryway to the back deck. Upstairs you’ll find comfortable bedrooms, a formal dining room & a wood burning fireplace in the living room! Abundant light & a thoughtful layout combined with a magnificent backyard will keep you cozy through all the seasons. Back deck has bluetooth speakers that turn on with the switch inside the backdoor. Inside is wired for Alexa capabilities. With ample space & a prime location, this home will give you plenty of room to live, work & thrive.
